  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Okay, this time, I'm even more ambitious! Want to help me with my third-ever alchemy experiment?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thank you very much. Can you bring me #b1 #t4010107##k, #b20 #t4000050#s#k, and #b10 #t2012002##k? I think I might be able to create a mysterious Scroll..."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Well, now. If you don't have time to listen to a poor girl's plea... Fine, just let me know if you change your mind."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ah! You got me #b1 #t4010107##k, #b20 #t4000050#s#k, and #b10 #t2012002##k. Whew, I need a minute to mentally prepare myself..."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "While I do this, make sure you have an empty slot in your Use inventory. Okay, okay, breathe, breathe. Steady hands, and mix, and pour, and..."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Oh my. Oh my goodness. OH MY! I am sooooo talented! Look! I made a #rscroll for gloves#k! I think I'm going to faint from happiness. I couldn't have done it without you, so here, take it. It's yours."
        }
      },
